quran[8{c,v,t}:
11,38,"Nooh kashti bana raha tha aur is ki qoum ke sardaro mein se jo koi is ke paas se guzarta tha woh is ka mazaq urata tha is ne kaha"" agar tum hum par hanstay ho to hum bhi tum par hans rahay hain"
11,39,"anqareeb tumhe khud maloom ho jaye ga ke kis par woh azaab aata hai jo ussay ruswa kar day ga aur kis par woh bulaa toot padtee hai jo talaay nah talle gi """
11,40,"yahan taq ke jab hamara hukum agaya aur woh tano ray ubal para to hum ne kaha"" har qisam ke janwaron ka aik aik jora kashti mein rakh lau, apne ghar walon ko bhi siwaye unn ashkhaas ke jin ki nishaan dahi pehlay ki ja chuki hai is mein sawaar kara do aur un logon ko bhi bitha lau jo imaan laaye hain"" aur thoray hi log thay jo Nooh ke sath imaan laaye thay"
11,41,"Nooh ne kaha"" sawaar ho jao iss mein, Allah hi ke naam se hai is ka chalna bhi aur is ka therna bhi, mera rab bara ghafoor o Raheem hai """
11,42,"kashti un logon ko liye chali ja rahi thi aur aik aik mouj pahar ki terhan uth rahi thi Nooh ka beta daur faaslay par tha Nooh ne pukaar kar kaha"" beta, hamaray sath sawaar ho ja, kafiroon ke sath nah reh """
11,43,"uss ne palat kar jawab diya"" mein abhi aik pahar par charha jata hon jo mujhe pani se bacha le ga"" Nooh ne kaha, aaj koi cheez Allah ke hukum se bachanay wali nahi hai siwaye iss ke ke Allah hi kisi par reham farmaiye"" itnay mein aik mouj dono ke darmain haail ho gayi aur woh bhi doobnay walon mein shaamil ho gaya"
11,44,"hukum howa"" ae zameen, apna sara pani nigal ja aur ae aasman, ruk ja"" chunancha pani zameen mein baith gaya, faisla chuka diya gaya, kashti Jodi par tik gayi, aur keh diya gaya ke daur hui zaalmon ki qoum !"
11,45,"Nooh ne apne rab ko puraka kaha"" ae rab, mera beta mere ghar walon mein se hai aur tera wada sacha hai aur to sab hakmon se bara aur behtar haakim hai """
